OL,7,FRichard "Alex" Murdaugh, the disgraced
OL,8,FSouth Carolina lawyer who was found
OL,9,Fguilty of killing his wife and son has
OL,10,Fbeen sentenced to life behind bars,
OL,11,Fdespite making a last-minute appeal
OL,12,Fprotesting his innocence.
OL,14,FAt a hearing on Friday, Circuit Court
OL,15,FJudge Clifton Newman sentenced Murdaugh
OL,16,Fto prison for the remainder of his
OL,17,Fnatural life, criticising his
OL,18,F"duplicitious conduct", which he said
OL,19,Fwas especially troubling given the
OL,20,Ffamily's long history as lawyers and
OL,21,Fprosecutors in the region.
